Class Kabasuji

  • java.lang.Object
    • odysseus.Kabasuji
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Builder, Player

    public abstract class Kabasuji
extends java.lang.Object
    Kabasuji is the super class to both Builder and Player. The Kabasuji class is responsible for the container and doing and undoing moves.
    Author:
    Carlos Barcelos
